00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:05,650
Dangerous Guys Are Coming

22
00:02:00,610 --> 00:02:08,300


23
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:10,850
It's looking more and
 more like a ballpark.

24
00:02:10,850 --> 00:02:15,000
We'll finally be able to use our
 ballpark starting next week, right ?

25
00:02:16,050 --> 00:02:18,510
Our ballpark...!

26
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:50,800
Private School - Senkawa High School

27
00:02:52,890 --> 00:02:58,060
Guys, we have our opponent for
the ballpark commemoration game.

28
00:02:58,060 --> 00:03:00,320
Which team is it, Captain ?

29
00:03:01,450 --> 00:03:04,430
It's a team that made it to the quarterfinals in the summer tournament last year.

30
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:07,970
Oh, I'm surprised that a good team like that has accepted to play us.

31
00:03:07,970 --> 00:03:09,700
So which one is it ?

32
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,940
Hiryuu West.

33
00:03:11,940 --> 00:03:12,990
What ?!

34
00:03:13,710 --> 00:03:14,910
What the heck ?!

35
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:17,650
It's supposed to be the memorable first game for our baseball team.

36
00:03:17,650 --> 00:03:20,500
 But of all the teams, 
Hiryuu West is our opponent ?

37
00:03:42,860 --> 00:03:45,680
Is there a problem ?

38
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,200
You don't know ?

39
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:53,700
They're a violent team that was barred for a year for an in-game brawling incident.

40
00:03:56,890 --> 00:04:00,540
That suspension just ended recently.

41
00:04:00,540 --> 00:04:03,400
Apparently, they've been
 looking for a practice partner...

42
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:06,450
...but haven't been able to find one, and they've been in need of help.

43
00:04:06,450 --> 00:04:10,000
Of course ! 
Hiryuu West is notoriously bad !

44
00:04:10,310 --> 00:04:13,120
I hear they bean people like crazy.

45
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:16,500
Wasn't the reason for the brawl also because of a bean ball ?

46
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:22,260
That's right. They hit somebody, and yet
 they got mad when someone complained.

47
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:25,640
I might get a fever
 and miss the game...

48
00:04:26,210 --> 00:04:30,070
You shouldn't judge 
people by a rumor.

49
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:32,310
I guess, but...

50
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:35,910
They did actually
 get suspended, after all.

51
00:04:35,910 --> 00:04:39,730
No, there are no bad 
people who play baseball.

52
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,570
But...

53
00:04:41,570 --> 00:04:43,150
Yeah...

54
00:04:43,150 --> 00:04:44,490
Don't worry.

55
00:04:53,710 --> 00:04:58,430
I have a plan, just in case. You shouldn't worry.

56
00:04:58,430 --> 00:04:59,320
That's all.


57
00:05:04,330 --> 00:05:06,430
He doesn't seem like an ordinary guy.

58
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:07,310
Right.

59
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:11,050
He disappears without 
watching us practice.

60
